          close signals during calls
          <br />
          ðŸš€ Orbit Pulse: Tracks candidate job changes, promotions, and availability
          <br />
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a
            href="/orbit-signal"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            Try Orbit Signal
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
  }
  .fade-in svg {
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
